branch
    Independent line of development in a project
    default branch : master or main

======== creating a new branch ============
to view all the branches
git branch

to create new branch
git branch new_feature

to select or switch to the branch
git checkout new_feature 

to create and swtich to new branch
git checkout -b latest_branch

to delete a branch
git checkout master
git branch -d <branch_name>
    It deletes right away if nothing is there to merge or gives an error

================ Merging ============
    combines the branced data and history together
git checkout master

git merge new_feature
    2 branches points to the same commit

=========== Merge conflict ================
if same line is updated in 2 different branches and if we tried to merge , it gives merge conflict
